mpu:</p><ol data-start=\"486\" data-end=\"688\"><li data-section-id=\"ydwkys\" data-start=\"486\" data-end=\"524\"><p data-start=\"488\" data-end=\"524\">Memahami konsep dasar kewirausahaan.</p></li><li data-section-id=\"1wsgthl\" data-start=\"525\" data-end=\"558\"><p data-start=\"527\" data-end=\"558\">Mengidentifikasi peluang usaha.</p></li><li data-section-id=\"1b8tkrj\" data-start=\"559\" data-end=\"595\"><p data-start=\"561\" data-end=\"595\">Menyusun rencana bisnis sederhana.</p></li><li data-section-id=\"gilarj\" data-start=\"596\" data-end=\"628\"><p data-start=\"598\" data-end=\"628\">Menerapkan strategi pemasaran.</p></li><li data-section-id=\"19k2fem\" data-start=\"629\" data-end=\"656\"><p data-start=\"631\" data-end=\"656\">Mengelola keuangan usaha.</p></li><li data-section-id=\"1ti47l2\" data-start=\"657\" data-end=\"688\"><p data-start=\"659\" data-end=\"688\">Mengevaluasi kelayakan usaha.</p></li></ol>','Kewirausahaan','','publish','closed','closed','','kewirausahaan','','','2026-06-16 13:13:02','2026-06-16 13:13:02','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=courses&#038;p=965',0,'courses','',0),(966,1,'2026-06-02 12:24:24','2026-06-02 12:24:24','','Checkout','','draft','closed','closed','','lp-checkout','','','2026-06-16 13:40:09','2026-06-16 13:40:09','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/lp-checkout/',0,'page','',0),(967,1,'2026-06-02 12:24:24','2026-06-02 12:24:24','<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[tutor_dashboard]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode -->','Profile','','publish','closed','closed','','lp-profile','','','2026-06-16 13:45:20','2026-06-16 13:45:20','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/lp-profile/',0,'page','',0),(968,1,'2026-06-02 12:24:24','2026-06-02 12:24:24','','Courses','','publish','closed','closed','','courses','','','2026-06-16 11:53:13','2026-06-16 11:53:13','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/courses/',0,'page','',0),(969,1,'2026-06-02 12:24:24','2026-06-02 12:24:24','<!-- wp:shortcode -->[learn_press_instructors]<!-- /wp:shortcode -->','Instructors','','dra