i menyediakan berbagai mata kuliah yang dilengkapi dengan materi, latihan, penugasan, dan presensi pada setiap pertemuan.</p><p data-start=\"388\" data-end=\"575\">Melalui LMS ini, mahasiswa dapat mengakses materi pembelajaran secara terstruktur, mengikuti latihan, mengerjakan tugas, serta mengisi daftar hadir sesuai dengan mata kuliah yang dipilih.</p><p data-start=\"388\" data-end=\"575\"> </p><h2 data-section-id=\"1ddmt2i\" data-start=\"870\" data-end=\"891\">Daftar Mata Kuliah</h2><h3 data-section-id=\"7w98mz\" data-start=\"893\" data-end=\"913\">1. Kewirausahaan</h3><h3 data-section-id=\"1h6y5jk\" data-start=\"1013\" data-end=\"1029\">2. Pancasila</h3><h3 data-section-id=\"1h6y5jk\" data-start=\"1013\" data-end=\"1029\">3. Matematika Dasar</h3><h3 data-section-id=\"g1lw61\" data-start=\"1254\" data-end=\"1281\">4. Profesi Kependidikan</h3><h3 data-section-id=\"1nou3dv\" data-start=\"1361\" data-end=\"1402\">5. Manajemen dan Administrasi Sekolah</h3>','Halaman Utama','','trash','closed','closed','','new-course__trashed','','','2026-06-15 12:34:17','2026-06-15 12:34:17','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=courses&#038;p=1046',0,'courses','',0),(1047,1,'2026-06-15 12:35:21','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','closed','closed','','','','','2026-06-15 12:35:21','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=1047',0,'page','',0),(1048,1,'2026-06-15 12:39:34','2026-06-15 12:39:34','{\"fields\":{\"1\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"type\":\"text\",\"label\":\"Nama Mahasiswa\",\"description\":\"\",\"size\":\"medium\",\"placeholder\":\"\",\"limit_count\":\"1\",\"limit_mode\":\"characters\",\"default_value\":\"\",\"input_mask\":\"\",\"css\":\"\"},\"2\":{\"id\":\"2\",\"type\":\"text\",\"label\":\"Nim\",\"description\":\"\",\"size\":\"medium\",\"placeholder\":\"\",\"limit_count\":\"1\",\"limit_mode\":\"characters\",\"default_value\":\"\",\"input_mask\":\"\",\"css\":\"\"},\"3\":{\"id\":\"3\",\"type\":\"select\",\"label\":\"Mata Kuliah\",\"choices